<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_270_r2l20"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> vns ſeyn ʒwen <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> brıef neẅlıchen <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_270_r2l21">wır ʒu <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan> maſſ <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd ſeyn vns etwıeuıl <expan>derſelbe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_270_r2l22">meͣr kleglıch ʒu hörn vnd mıt <expan>treẅe<ex>n</ex></expan> laıd / Vnd als Jr vns von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_270_r2l23"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ des <expan>Römiſch<ex>en</ex></expan> etc künıgs ʒukunft <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_270_r2l24">habt <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>ſchreıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> Alſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır ſeıd der <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_270_r2l25">wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>freẅntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> nehſt getan <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . niht <expan>treffenlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> mer <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_270_r2l26"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> Doch ſo ſeyn <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dıe Bıſchof von Paſſaw vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_270_r2l27">~ von Maylan / der Patrıarch von fryawl vnd ~ der <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> von vvein = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_270_r2l28">ſperg noch bey vns dıe ſeinr <expan>künıgl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒukunft noch alls <expan>warte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_270_r2l29">als wır <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> / Denn von des <expan>Salpet<ex>er</ex>s</expan> vnd ſwefels <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> den </ab>
