</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns seyn zwen <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        brief newlichen <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>, die wir zu <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        mass <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>; und seyn uns etwievil
                                <expan>derselbe<ex>n</ex></expan> meͣr kleglich zu hörn und mit
                                <expan>trewe<ex>n</ex></expan> laid. Und als ir uns von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan> etc.
                        künigs zukunft <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> czu <expan>schreibe<ex>n</ex></expan>, also
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir seid der
                            <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>, die wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> nehst getan
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, niht
                            <expan>treffenlich<ex>er</ex></expan> mer <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>. Doch so seyn <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, die bischof von Passaw und von Maylan, der
                        patriarch von Fryawl und der <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> von Weinsperg
                        noch bey uns, die seinr <expan>künigl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zukunft noch alls
                            <expan>warte<ex>n</ex></expan>, als wir
                        <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan>. Denn von des
                            <expan>salpet<ex>er</ex>s</expan> und swefels
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, den wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> bey uns kawft
                        <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, da <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> etlich
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> frewnde vor x
                            <expan>tag<ex>en</ex></expan> ein für bey uns gefunden und <add>in</add>
<expan>denselbe<ex>n</ex></expan> zewg <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
                        ewch <expan>zu bring<ex>en</ex></expan>, als auch wir
                                <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz er <pb facs="#facs_271" id="134v"/>ewch
                        nu <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> sey; <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> frewnde <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> ein
                                <expan>rechnu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> gemacht, was
                                <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> zewg kost, als ir an der zettel
                        hierynn <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sloss<ex>en</ex></expan> wol
                                <expan>verneme<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>det</expan>; dasselb gelt mugt ir den zweyen
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>geselle<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hawbtlewte<ex>n</ex></expan> bey ewch wol
                            <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> und geben. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewer<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
